public class LockedExit extends Tile

  • Constructor Details

    • LockedExit

      public LockedExit(Maze.Point tilePos)
      Default constructor, sets the position and color of the tile, and obstructiveness to true. An observer is also added to the player so that the obstructiveness is updated based on the treasures collected. The same observer makes sure that when they are on this tile, it is reset.
      Parameters:
      tilePos - Point to set the position field to.
